<section xml:id="sec-cleaning-is-important" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <title>Cleaning is Important</title>

  <introduction>
    <p>
      Cleaning is the arguable most important part of staying safe during a production. Although, 
      at the end of the day you almost always want to leave as soon as possible, taking the time 
      to clean up and put things away is the best thing to do. I have 3 official reasons, but 
      honestly it doesn't take much time and the shop won't have to look like the mess in the 
      images here.
    </p>
